Lenglet: &quot;Griezmann? I'm not strong enough in the club to ask my opinion on these decisions. In any case, they never asked me about him.&quot;<br />
<br />
&quot;Umtiti and I play in the same position, on the same club and now in France, people inevitably ask questions, try to compare. I always give the same answer because it is the truth: The relationship has been very good between us since I arrived.&quot;

Philippe Coutinho: &quot;I have not had a good season, I have not managed to do what the people and I expected.&quot; [via sport]<br />
